title: Red Electrick - Young Again 720P [Video]
description:
Red Electrik are a very popular Maltese Rock Band, who's talent is largely unknown World Wide.   This song could of easily become an International Number One hit but for the fact that the Music Industry has totally lost it's way in finding new talent and promoting it sigh...

This is a very emotive and classy Video which tells a powerful tale of a subject we will all study only too well.  I have left the end credits in just on the off chance that some person in Europe or North America will re issue this former number one hit from 2014 and get this group the World stage they deserve.

Yes there is more to pop than Pitbull, Rap and Hip hop!!!!
